Package: FISHmQC
Type: Package
Title: Performs barcode-decoding quality control for FISH-based spatial transcriptomic runs
Version: 1.0
Date: 2026-05-11
Author: Michael Barkasi
Maintainer: Michael Barkasi <barkasi@wustl.edu>
Description: Estimates the proportion of barcodes correctly decoded (i.e., "precision") in FISH-based spatial transcriptomics runs by estimating bit-flip rates using blank counts and dichotomized Gaussians.
License: GPL 3
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.13), RcppEigen, dplyr
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppEigen
Depends: ggplot2, grid, gridExtra, colorspace
SystemRequirements: NLopt
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
